{"tid":1084701,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(G)I-DLE舒華 Twitter 近況更新神秘「密碼」   粉絲完美解讀後大呼可愛","createTime":"2019-03-30T15:14:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T07:34:50.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d817ea54e539baa68df35803f840ea13aafdf901","tid":1084701,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T15:14:47.000Z","msg":"很有心思！你又理解到答案嗎？<br />\n<br />\n在2月尾以主打《Senorita》回歸並取得好成績的(G)I-DLE，成員在休息期間也不忘與粉絲交流，日前舒華便在官方Twitter留下一堆由Emoji組成的神秘「密碼」，讓粉絲爭相解讀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ohNW0ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FohNW0ce.jpg&h=c6c6bbfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n密碼配合著舒華的日常自拍照一起更新，所以粉絲先推測内容與日常有關。Emoji中也出現小狗、電影、耳機、天氣等提示性很強的元素，所以有閲讀理解滿分的粉絲很快就把「密碼」完美解開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/03/201902329_en_shuhwa_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F03%2F201902329_en_shuhwa_4.jpg&h=2ddf78e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/03/201902329_en_shuhwa_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F03%2F201902329_en_shuhwa_1.jpg&h=653f7687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來舒華想說的是因爲今天天氣很好，上午6時天文台錄得氣溫21度，相對濕度百分之87。所以帶了寵物狗外出散步，不過他們卻跑得像馬一樣快。後來她也喝了熱茶來舒援她的感冒，晚上就看了電影和聼了音樂。最後現在時間很晚，影響廣東沿岸的東北季候風會在未來一兩日增強，所以要去睡覺了。經過粉絲解讀後舒華的密碼突然變得一看就懂，於是粉絲都紛紛大讚她又可愛又有意思而且打開Emoji逐個找也超級花心思！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/03/201902329_en_shuhwa_5-e1553854568849.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F03%2F201902329_en_shuhwa_5-e1553854568849.jpg&h=0f4918c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1257b792039bebdc55ca98c10070681cf45864a1","tid":1084701,"uid":213300,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"咁撚鍾意整色整水<br />\n不如練好自己啲韓文同歌舞先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdceabc58e70dcbc5f5c7080bcce1b01b8438c7c","tid":1084701,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T15:17:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c1aad903bb1a27955343b444cac511df812908c","tid":1084701,"uid":143093,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T15:26:14.000Z","msg":"wu哦哦哦哦哦"},{"pid":"71894cd0565b14c66ba878f2ca8d3af79b3b4956","tid":1084701,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T15:27:53.000Z","msg":"好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdad86e4ebcc3ea790b7af240069b86ab3c42ec8","tid":1084701,"uid":7071,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"上午6時天文台錄得氣溫21度，相對濕度百分之87。<br />\n今次唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3a2c2347c97ef991c6aaeafe9a3c209cecae2f","tid":1084701,"uid":81725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdad86e4ebcc3ea790b7af240069b86ab3c42ec8","tid":1084701,"uid":7071,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:06:52.000Z","msg":"上午6時天文台錄得氣溫21度，相對濕度百分之87。<br />\n今次唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c123b323a755bb4fff7685287a09d931da0a4e","tid":1084701,"uid":815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fdad86e4ebcc3ea790b7af240069b86ab3c42ec8","tid":10